  "title": "Waste Truck Driver",
  "description": "<p>🚛 <strong>Job Description – Truck Driver (Waste Collection Services)</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Drive assigned trucks to project sites to carry out scheduled waste collection services</li>\n  <li>Transport refuse to designated incineration plants for disposal</li>\n  <li>Operate various truck systems including <strong>Hook-lift</strong>, <strong>REL</strong>, and <strong>Erose</strong> for efficient waste collection</li>\n  <li>Perform <strong>crew duties</strong> when required, especially during manpower shortages or as assigned by the reporting officer</li>\n  <li>Ensure proper loading, unloading, and handling of waste containers</li>\n  <li>Adhere to all road safety regulations and company policies</li>\n</ul>\n<p>✅ <strong>Job Requirements </strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Must hold a valid <strong>Class 4 Driving License</strong> (Singapore)</li>\n  <li>Strong and responsible driving skills with a clean driving record</li>\n  <li>Good knowledge of traffic laws and safety regulations</li>\n  <li>Responsible, cooperative, and able to work well in a team setting</li>\n  <li>WSQ certificate in <strong>(PI-WM-106E-1)</strong> is an added advantage</li>\n  <li>Physically fit and capable of handling demanding tasks in an outdoor environment</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
